node.text:
Today we're proud to highlight our Sierra Sister Sessions, a series of outdoor-sports focused events created to celebrate women and support local organizations. To kick off the series, we partnered with the Changing Tides Foundation in Southern California and gathered for live music, a beach clean-up, and some killer surfing. 🏄🏽‍♀️ 

Check out @changingtidesfoundation to learn more about their work to protect the planet and promote inclusivity in the ocean and beyond. Stay tuned for info about upcoming #SierraSisterSessions. 

🎥 @hannahwalsh7 

#WomensEqualityDay
